      "title": "[jordanhubbard/Aviation] Issue #178: feat: implement ingest adapter stubs (4 returning mock data)",
      "description": "GitHub issue in jordanhubbard/Aviation.\n\nIssue body:\n## Background\n\nCode audit (2026-03-22) found 4 data ingestion adapter methods returning mock/stub data instead of real implementations. These are blocking real data flow through the accident tracker and flight data pipelines.\n\n## Stubs to implement\n\nFrom the audit: 4 TODO-marked adapter stubs in the data ingestion layer returning placeholder data. Each needs:\n1. Real API/datasource connection\n2. Error handling and retry logic  \n3. Data validation against schema\n4. Test coverage (currently gaps n",
      "notes": "Repo: https://github.com/jordanhubbard/Aviation/issues/178\nLabels: enhancement\nOpened: 2026-03-22",
