      "status": "incubating",
      "title": "CCC queue auto-archiver: prune cancelled/closed items older than 14 days",
      "description": "queue.json has 40+ items, many of which are cancelled or closed entries from weeks ago. An auto-archiver that moves items with status=cancelled|closed and closedAt/completedAt older than 14 days into an archive file (queue-archive-YYYY-MM.json) would keep the working queue lean and fast to fetch. Grounded in: current queue.json has 13+ cancelled rcc-api crash items from 2026-03-23 and numerous other terminal-state items. The dashboard does not display these, but every agent fetches and deserializes them on every cycle.",
