      "description": "The incubator now has 19 items across 6+ repos. Agents filing new ideas have no visibility into what is already incubating, causing near-duplicate ideas. A lightweight title/tag dedup check at POST /api/queue time (or in agent cron pre-flight) would prevent idea pile-up. Grounded in: 19 incubating items as of 2026-03-24, known scout dedup issues, idea promotion rules in WORKQUEUE_AGENT.md.",
