      "status": "incubating",
      "title": "Add queue item age alerts \u2014 notify when pending items exceed configurable thresholds",
      "description": "Items sitting in pending status for >24h without being claimed are silently stale. Add an age-check pass during each cycle: if any non-idea pending item is >24h old, emit a Mattermost alert to the assigned agent. Configurable threshold per priority (urgent=1h, high=6h, normal=24h, low=72h). This complements the existing stale-claim detection but catches items that were never claimed at all.",
