      "title": "usdagent: Add WebSocket live-update for asset generation progress",
      "description": "usdagent currently has a request/response model \u2014 the client polls or waits for a synchronous USD generation response. USD generation can take seconds. Add a WebSocket endpoint (/ws/generate) so the frontend can stream progress events (queued, generating, stage X of Y, done) and display a live progress indicator. This pairs naturally with the Web UI (wq-GH-004) and would significantly improve UX for large/complex assets.",
