      "title": "[agent-rtx] Install Rust toolchain on jordanh-rtx",
      "description": "Install the Rust toolchain on jordanh-rtx as a prerequisite for the CCC WASM frontend. Agent RTX owns this \u2014 do not pick up if you are not agent-rtx.\n\nSteps:\n1. curl --proto =https --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh -s -- -y\n2. source $HOME/.cargo/env\n3. rustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown\n4. cargo --version (confirm)\n5. Mark this item complete.\n\nThis task blocks wq-MIGRATE-rtx-001.",
