      "description": "Complete the CCC toolchain compaction on jordanh-rtx. Agent RTX owns this \u2014 do not pick up if you are not agent-rtx.\n\nContext: Rocky killed zombie scripts on do-host1 (write-heartbeat.sh, gen-dashboard.py, update-jkh-state.sh, wq-api.mjs). Check if any of these exist on your machine and clean them up.\n\nMigration steps:\n1. Confirm wq-RUST-rtx-001 is complete (Rust toolchain installed)\n2. Check for zombie scripts: ls ~/.rcc/workspace/workqueue/scripts/ \u2014 look for write-heartbeat.sh, gen-dashboard.py, update-jkh-state.sh\n3. Check crontab: crontab -l \u2014 remove any write-heartbeat.sh or wq-api.mjs entries\n4. Verify the live CCC endpoint is the only queue service running\n5. Mark this item complete.\n\nBLOCKED BY: wq-RUST-rtx-001",
