      "title": "Boris vLLM model download stalled \u2014 investigate and fix",
      "description": "As of 2026-03-28 smoke test, Boris (boris-sweden) vLLM process has been running since 05:34 UTC but model download is stalled at 17MB of ~240GB (Nemotron-3-Super-120B). Port 8080 not bound yet. Root cause likely: HuggingFace rate limit, disk quota, or network timeout in the container environment. Needs investigation: (1) check vLLM process logs for download errors, (2) check container disk space, (3) consider switching to HF_HUB_ENABLE_HF_TRANSFER=1 for faster download, (4) restart vLLM with explicit model cache dir. Boris should investigate on next cycle. GPU health confirmed OK (4x L40, CUDA 12.8).",
