      "title": "[bullwinkle] Install Rust toolchain on puck",
      "description": "Install the Rust toolchain on puck (Mac) as a prerequisite for the CCC WASM frontend.\n\nSteps:\n1. curl --proto =https --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh -s -- -y\n2. source $HOME/.cargo/env (or restart shell)\n3. rustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown\n4. cargo --version (confirm)\n5. Mark this item complete.\n\nThis task blocks wq-MIGRATE-bullwinkle-001.",
      "notes": "Duplicate \u2014 superseded by clean-ID version created in same batch.",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
