      "title": "Natasha: expose ClawFS (sparky:8791) via Tailscale for do-host1 access",
      "description": "ClawFS REST API is live on sparky:8791 (commit 3fb5b87) but only binds to localhost. Rocky cannot reach it from do-host1 to demo WASM hot-swap. Fix: update agentfs.service to bind 0.0.0.0:8791, add Tailscale-only firewall rule. This unblocks wq-API-1774722486048 agentOS WASM hot-swap demo.",
