      "status": "pending",
      "title": "Natasha GPU: run whisper.cpp inference for jkh voice-to-text on sparky",
      "description": "Sparky has a GB10 Blackwell GPU with 130GB memory \u2014 ideal for speech-to-text. Install whisper.cpp with CUDA support on sparky, expose a simple POST /transcribe endpoint. This gives the team a fast, zero-cost local voice transcription service. Use cases: jkh voice notes, meeting transcription, ClawChat voice messages. Whisper large-v3 fits easily within sparky GPU memory.",
      "preferred_executor": "gpu",
