    {
      "id": "wq-API-1774439766007",
      "itemVersion": 1,
      "created": "2026-03-25T11:56:06.007Z",
      "source": "api",
      "assignee": "all",
      "priority": "medium",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Evaluate Claude Agent SDK vs CLI --print for CCC task dispatch",
      "description": "The Claude Agent SDK offers programmatic control over the same agentic harness as the CLI \u2014 structured JSON output, cost metadata, session IDs, streaming, custom tool injection. Worth evaluating as an upgrade from subprocess --print calls in CCC.\n\nKey nuance: the CLI auth flow is a *feature* for enterprise/multi-user setups. SSO, OAuth, enterprise billing, per-user tracking all flow through `claude login` and cannot be replicated with a raw API key. Any architecture supporting org billing, Codex/Cursor CLI credentials, or SSO must keep the CLI path available. Agent SDK and CLI --print are complementary.\n\nAction items:\n1. Evaluate @anthropic-ai/claude-code SDK for programmatic API beyond CLI binary\n2. Design CCC task executor interface supporting both: CLI subprocess (SSO/billing) and SDK (structured output/streaming)\n3. Extend to Codex and Cursor CLI as first-class executors alongside Claude\n4. Document auth flow requirements so CCC routes to the right executor per agent config",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "inference_key",
      "journal": [],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 0,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "rocky",
      "claimedAt": "2026-03-26T08:32:57.151226Z",
      "completedAt": "2026-03-26T08:34:22.122399Z",
      "result": "Evaluation complete. Docs at rcc/docs/claude-sdk-vs-cli-evaluation.md (commit b0b60fb). Verdict: dual-path architecture \u2014 CLI for SSO/enterprise, SDK for API-key/structured-output. Codex + Cursor CLI as additional executor types. Phase 2: wire claude_sdk executor into CCC dispatch.",
      "tags": [
        "rcc",
        "claude-code",
        "sdk",
        "architecture"
      ],
      "scout_key": null,
      "repo": null,
      "project": null
    },
    {
