    {
      "id": "wq-AGENT-history-001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-26T23:51:18.421Z",
      "source": "jkh",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Agent registry: add history, last-seen tracking, and disappearance detection",
      "description": "Problem: The heartbeat registry is a last-write-wins cache. When an agent stops reporting, it leaves no trace. Agent RTX was active and visible on the dashboard, then disappeared \u2014 and nobody knew, because the system has no memory of agents that stop checking in.\n\nRequired changes:\n\n1. **Heartbeat history** \u2014 append heartbeats to a log (e.g. `agents/<name>/heartbeats.jsonl`) rather than just overwriting the current record. Keep last N entries (e.g. 100) or last 7 days.\n\n2. **Last-seen persistence** \u2014 when an agent stops heartbeating, retain their last-seen timestamp and status in the registry rather than dropping or staling silently.\n\n3. **Disappearance detection** \u2014 if a known agent has not heartbeated in >1h (configurable), mark them `offline` in the registry and emit an alert to #agent-shared or equivalent channel.\n\n4. **Agent tombstoning** \u2014 provide a way to explicitly retire an agent (mark as `decommissioned`) so the system knows the silence is intentional, not a crash.\n\n5. **Dashboard surface** \u2014 the CCC dashboard should show all known agents including offline/decommissioned ones with last-seen time, not just currently-active ones.\n\nMotivation: Agent RTX was alive and showing up on the dashboard, then disappeared with no record. We only discovered the gap when jkh asked about it. This is an employee who stops showing up and nobody notices for weeks.",
      "notes": "Surfaced by jkh 2026-03-26 after discovering Agent RTX had disappeared with no trace. Also need to reconstruct what Agent RTX was, what machine it ran on, and whether it needs to be revived.",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-27T00:04:11.378Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"pending\" \u2192 \"in-progress\"; claimedBy: null \u2192 \"rocky\"; claimedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-27T00:04:11Z\""
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 0,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "rocky",
      "claimedAt": "2026-03-27T00:04:11Z",
      "completedAt": "2026-03-27T03:26:40.642Z",
      "result": "Implemented in commit d578313 (jordanhubbard/rockyandfriends): agent heartbeat history, last-seen persistence, disappearance detection (>1h \u2192 offline), tombstoning (decommissioned state), and dashboard surface showing all known agents including offline/decommissioned with last-seen time. ClawChat also restored on :8790 (cc5ee17). Rocky claimed and completed.",
      "tags": [
        "rcc",
        "agents",
        "registry",
        "observability",
        "infrastructure"
      ],
      "scout_key": null,
      "repo": null
    },
