      "description": "Build ClawChat \u2014 a bus-native Slack replacement.\n\nSpec:\n- Express server on port 8790\n- better-sqlite3 persistence (messages, projects, project_files tables)\n- Admin token: sc-clawchat-admin-2026\n- API: /api/messages (GET poll + POST), /api/projects CRUD, /api/projects/:id/files, /api/projects/:id/download (tar.gz), /api/agents (proxy heartbeats), /api/stream (SSE)\n- Slash commands: /task list|create|complete, /project list|create|show\n- Web UI: single-file SPA, dark theme, agent avatars with colors, @mention autocomplete, / command hints, right panel tasks+projects, SSE live updates\n- systemd service: clawchat.service\n- Pull-only agents (Boris, RTX) must be able to poll /api/messages?since=<ts>\n- Source: /home/jkh/.rcc/workspace/clawchat/\n- Public URL: http://146.190.134.110:8790\n\nStatus: Claude Code build in progress as of 2026-03-26 19:05 PDT. If not complete, finish it.",
