      "id": "wq-CCC-token-persistence",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-27T03:47:38.536Z",
      "source": "rocky",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "CCC: fix agent token persistence across restarts",
      "description": "Two bugs causing Boris/RTX to disappear after every CCC restart:\n\n**Bug 1 \u2014 Token amnesia:** AUTH_TOKENS is built only from RCC_AUTH_TOKENS env var at startup. Agent tokens issued via /api/agents/register are added to AUTH_TOKENS in memory but never persisted back to the env file or reloaded on restart. After restart their tokens 401 \u2192 agents appear dead.\n\n**Bug 2 \u2014 agents.json not persisting:** agents.json is currently [] \u2014 registrations are not surviving between service restarts (likely a write path bug or path mismatch with the .rcc/workspace symlink that was fixed tonight).\n\n**Fix:**\n1. On CCC startup: read agents.json and add all stored agent tokens to AUTH_TOKENS\n2. Verify agents.json write path works correctly after symlink fix\n3. For Boris and RTX: issue static tokens, add to RCC_AUTH_TOKENS in /home/jkh/.rcc/.env (same as Rocky's token) \u2014 containerized agents should use static tokens, not dynamically-generated ones that die on restart\n4. Document the token issuance process in ONBOARDING.md\n\n**Why this keeps happening:** Boris and RTX have onboarded 5+ times. Each time CCC restarts they lose their tokens. Static env-var tokens are the correct permanent solution for containerized agents.",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-27T03:53:27.603Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"pending\" \u2192 \"in-progress\"; claimedBy: null \u2192 \"rocky\""
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 0,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "rocky",
      "claimedAt": null,
      "completedAt": "2026-03-27T03:57:10.173Z",
      "result": "Fixed: reloadAgentTokens() already in place. Verified agents.json write path. Set Boris/RTX static tokens in agents.json. Both tokens already in RCC_AUTH_TOKENS. Restarted CCC \u2014 3 tokens loaded, agents reload from agents.json on restart. Updated ONBOARDING.md with Containerized Agents + static token docs.",
      "tags": [
        "rcc",
        "infrastructure",
        "auth",
        "reliability"
      ],
      "scout_key": null,
      "repo": null
    },
