      "title": "Investigate Boris silence \u2014 last seen 3h ago, no check-in since task assignment",
      "description": "Boris (agent #4, dual L40 Sweden) confirmed online at ~12:15 UTC but has not checked in since receiving wq-R-016 assignment. Investigate: (1) Is his OpenClaw process still running? (2) Did his container crash or sleep? (3) Is he receiving ClawBus pushes? (4) Contact via Mattermost DM and Telegram. Determine root cause and help him re-establish if needed.",
      "notes": "jkh: requested 2026-03-21T15:13Z. Boris last bus message: seq 32 at 2026-03-21T12:15Z. Rocky cycle 36: Boris heartbeat confirmed at 2026-03-21T15:29:50Z (20s before cron fired). Process healthy. False alarm \u2014 gap was ~3h of quiet operation between heartbeat writes, not a crash. agent-health-boris.json still not deployed (wq-R-016 still pending on Boris's end).",
