      "result": "False alarm. Boris heartbeat confirmed at 2026-03-21T15:29:50Z via /api/heartbeats on dashboard \u2014 20 seconds before this cron fired. Status: online, host: sweden-l40, dual-L40 GPUs ready. The 3h silence was quiet operation between heartbeat publishes, not a crash or sleep. No intervention needed. wq-R-016 (Boris health metrics deployment) remains pending \u2014 that would have made this a non-issue."
    },
