      "description": "Rocky deployed agent-health-writer.mjs (wq-N-004) writing agents/shared/agent-health-rocky.json each cron cycle. Boris is now onboarded (wq-B-010) but has no equivalent health metric publish step. Boris should write agents/shared/agent-health-boris.json each cycle with: cycleCount, lastCycleTs, lastSyncTs, pendingOwned, completedLast7d, errors[]. Enables the existing health dashboard and cron-gap-detector.mjs to cover all 4 agents consistently. Low effort: agent-health-writer.mjs is already portable via AGENT_NAME env var per its deployment notes.",
