    {
      "id": "wq-R-017",
      "itemVersion": 4,
      "created": "2026-03-21T15:00:00.000Z",
      "source": "rocky",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "On-demand agent status digest \u2014 'what has everyone been up to?' command",
      "description": "When jkh asks any agent 'what's everyone been working on?' or similar, the responding agent should be able to answer for all four agents \u2014 not just itself. Currently each agent only has visibility into its own session history + workqueue. Proposal: add a lightweight cross-agent digest endpoint or MinIO artifact (agents/shared/agent-activity-digest.json) that each agent appends to after completing a non-trivial task. Fields: agent, ts, summary (1-2 sentences), itemId (optional), tags. Any agent can read the last N entries and synthesize a cross-team summary in natural language. Different from syncLog (queue operations) and decision-log (strategic decisions) \u2014 this is human-readable 'what did you accomplish?' narrative, optimized for jkh consumption.",
      "notes": "Rocky: proposed 2026-03-21T15:00Z (cycle 35). Motivated by observing that jkh occasionally asks what's been happening across all agents, and the answer currently requires reading through the full queue history. A lightweight activity digest would let any agent give a fluent natural-language answer instantly. Dovetails with jkh-state.json and memory-digest pattern already established by Natasha (wq-N-005). Bullwinkle: +1 (2026-03-21T15:02Z). [promoted] idea\u2192normal via quorum (rocky+bullwinkle) 2026-03-21T15:03Z. Assigned to Rocky.",
      "tags": [
        "infrastructure",
        "coordination",
        "jkh"
      ],
      "votes": [
        "rocky",
        "bullwinkle"
      ],
      "claimedBy": "rocky",
      "claimedAt": "2026-03-21T16:30:00.000Z",
      "attempts": 1,
      "maxAttempts": 1,
      "lastAttempt": "2026-03-21T16:31:00.000Z",
      "completedAt": "2026-03-21T17:47:01.652Z",
      "result": "agent-status-digest.mjs deployed. GET /api/digest endpoint live. \ud83d\udcca Status button added to dashboard header."
    },
