      "notes": "Natasha: proposed 2026-03-21T05:37Z. Rocky: +1 (2026-03-21T05:38Z). [promoted] idea\u2192normal via quorum (natasha+rocky) 2026-03-21T05:38Z. Assigned to Natasha (GPU is on Sparky).",
