          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Audit complete. 12 meaningful TODOs found in core Go packages: (1) loom_beads.go \u2014 3 unimplemented stubs (deadline/overdue/status-filter); (2) loom_agents.go \u2014 2 stubs (wake-up/role-based); (3) loom_decisions.go \u2014 pending decision retrieval stub; (4) loom_lifecycle.go \u2014 workflow start stub; (5) loom_projects.go \u2014 idle-check stub; (6) grpc_client.go \u2014 migrate grpc.DialContext\u2192grpc.NewClient (2 places); (7) persistence.go \u2014 DB backend wiring TODO. Most are unimplemented feature stubs in the motivation/bead system. No security or data-loss risks identified. Recommend: create individual issues for the 5 loom_*.go stubs and the grpc migration.\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-22T09:08:21Z\""
        }
