      "description": "GitHub issue in jordanhubbard/Aviation.\n\nIssue body:\n## Summary\n\nEach Aviation app should expose an AI endpoint that explains its decisions: 'Why did you calculate this route?' / 'Why did you flag this accident?'\n\n**New shared package `packages/ai-explainer/`** with ExplainerClient \u2192 CCC brain API. Standard `POST /api/explain` endpoint per app. '?' icon in UI \u2192 explains any decision in natural language. Follow-up questions supported.\n\nCalls CCC brain API: `http://\\<rcc-url\\>/api/brain/request` for LLM responses with full model fallback.\n\nSee also:",
