      "description": "GitHub issue in jordanhubbard/Aviation.\n\nIssue body:\n## Background\n\nCode audit (2026-03-22) found 4 TODO-marked ForeFlight aircraft classification stubs. These affect how aircraft are categorized when importing ForeFlight data.\n\n## Stubs to implement\n\n4 classification methods with TODO markers. Need:\n1. Aircraft type classification logic (likely against FAA database or ForeFlight API response schema)\n2. Edge case handling (unknown aircraft types, experimental, etc.)\n3. Unit tests for each classification rule\n\n## Context\n\nForeFlight uses its own ai",
