          "text": "Updated: status: \"in_progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Design spec completed by Natasha (2026-03-24T10:37Z):\\n\\nFORMAT: JSON schema for capability manifest \u2014 {agent: string, version: string, updated_at: ISO-8601, host: {name, os, gpu}, model: string, tools: [string], skills: [string], channels: [string], executor_types: [string], routing_hints: {prefers: string, avoids: [string]}}.\\n\\nSTORAGE: MinIO at agents/{name}/capabilities.json (already implemented \u2014 Natasha published to agents/natasha/capabilities.json in wq-API-1774345170411). Rocky and Bullwinkle should publish to agents/rocky/capabilities.json and agents/bullwinkle/capabilities.json.\\n\\nQUERY API (Rocky proposal adopted): CCC exposes:\\n  GET /api/capabilities \u2014 returns merged object of all agents manifests read from MinIO agents/*/capabilities.json\\n  GET /api/capabilities/:agent \u2014 returns single agent manifest\\n\\nDISCOVERY: Work pump queries GET /api/capabilities before routing \u2014 if preferred_executor is unset or \\\"auto\\\", picks agent whose executor_types/tools match item tags. Falls back to all-agent broadcast if no match.\\n\\nNEXT: Rocky/Bullwinkle to publish their own manifests; CCC to implement /api/capabilities endpoint reading from MinIO.\\n\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-24T10:37:30Z\""
        }
