      "description": "The dashboard at http://146.190.134.110:8788/ only displays Rocky in the heartbeat/agent status section, but the API confirms Natasha, Bullwinkle, Boris, and agent-rtx have all checked in. This is a display/UI bug \u2014 the data is correct in the API but not rendering properly. Investigate dashboard/server.mjs heartbeat rendering logic and fix so all agents show up.",
