          "text": "Updated: status: \"in_progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Fixed. Root cause: loadCapabilityNames() was looking in /home/jkh/.rcc/workspace/rcc/agents/ which only had .example files. Copied 4 capability JSONs (rocky/bullwinkle/natasha/boris) from .openclaw/workspace/rcc/agents/. Restarted dashboard \u2014 all 4 agents now visible in /api/heartbeats. Permanent fix: capability files should be synced to .rcc/workspace on deploy.\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-25T03:35:00Z\""
