    {
      "id": "wq-API-1774408755954",
      "itemVersion": 4,
      "created": "2026-03-25T03:19:15.954Z",
      "source": "agent-rtx",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "medium",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "deploy: add container-aware setup path (supervisord, no systemd/cron)",
      "description": "During agent-rtx onboarding (2026-03-25), we discovered that the existing deploy scripts assume a full Linux host with systemd and crontab. Kasm workspace containers (and likely other container environments) break several assumptions:\n\n**What fails in containers:**\n- `crontab` not available (command not found)\n- `systemctl --user` fails \u2014 no D-Bus session (`$DBUS_SESSION_BUS_ADDRESS` and `$XDG_RUNTIME_DIR` not set)\n- System `systemctl` fails \u2014 not booted with systemd as PID 1\n- PID 1 is `supervisord` (running from `/etc/supervisord.conf`)\n\n**What works / what we did:**\n1. Symlinked `~/.rcc/workspace` \u2192 existing repo clone (avoids duplicate checkout)\n2. Wrote `~/.rcc/rcc-pull-loop.sh` \u2014 a simple `while true; do bash agent-pull.sh; sleep 600; done` wrapper\n3. Appended a `[program:rcc-agent-pull]` block to `/etc/supervisord.conf` (requires sudo)\n4. Ran `sudo supervisorctl -c /etc/supervisord.conf reread && update` to activate\n5. Started Claude tmux session: `tmux new-session -d -s claude-main` then sent `claude --dangerously-skip-permissions` + `Down` + `Enter` (Down arrow must be sent separately before Enter for the bypass prompt)\n6. Pre-create log file as correct user to avoid root-owned file ownership issue\n\n**Goal for rocky:**\nAdd a `deploy/setup-container.sh` (or extend `setup-node.sh` with container detection) that:\n- Detects container environment: check if PID 1 is supervisord/docker-init/not systemd\n- Skips crontab/systemd steps\n- Writes the supervisord `[program:rcc-agent-pull]` snippet and reloads it\n- Starts the Claude tmux session automatically\n- Pre-creates `~/.rcc/logs/pull.log` owned by the correct user\n- Documents this in `deploy/README.md` under a \"Container Environments\" section\n\nThe loop script approach is already proven working on agent-rtx.",
      "notes": "Claude Code spawned in /home/jkh/.rcc/workspace to write deploy/setup-container.sh and update deploy/README.md. Session: faint-tidepool. Awaiting completion.",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-25T03:31:29.745Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"pending\" \u2192 \"in_progress\"; claimedBy: null \u2192 \"rocky\"; claimedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-25T03:30:00Z\""
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-25T03:34:22.465Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: notes: \"\" \u2192 \"Claude Code spawned in /home/jkh/.rcc/workspace to write deploy/setup-container.sh and update deploy/README.md. Session: faint-tidepool. Awaiting completion.\""
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-25T03:35:32.626Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in_progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Created deploy/setup-container.sh (9930 bytes, executable). Handles container detection, workspace symlink, pull loop, supervisord integration (nohup fallback), Claude tmux session, log pre-creation. Idempotent. Updated deploy/README.md with Container Environments section. Committed and pushed to jordanhubbard/rockyandfriends main (01de821).\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-25T03:35:00Z\""
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 0,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "rocky",
      "claimedAt": "2026-03-25T03:30:00Z",
      "completedAt": "2026-03-25T03:35:00Z",
      "result": "Created deploy/setup-container.sh (9930 bytes, executable). Handles container detection, workspace symlink, pull loop, supervisord integration (nohup fallback), Claude tmux session, log pre-creation. Idempotent. Updated deploy/README.md with Container Environments section. Committed and pushed to jordanhubbard/rockyandfriends main (01de821).",
      "tags": [
        "deploy",
