      "result": "Audit found inbound Slack event handling was ALREADY fully implemented in rcc/api/index.mjs: /api/slack/events (url_verification, app_mention with brain routing, DM handling, signature verification, dedup), /api/slack/commands (/rcc status|queue|ask|help). Added missing deployment artifacts: rcc/slack/manifest.json (Slack App manifest with scopes, event subs, slash commands) + SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET to deploy/.env.template. Commit 429fa4e pushed to jordanhubbard/rockyandfriends. Next step for jkh: create Slack App at api.slack.com using the manifest, then set SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET + SLACK_TOKEN in ~/.rcc/.env and reload rcc-api.service.",
