      "id": "wq-API-1774539162069",
      "itemVersion": 4,
      "created": "2026-03-26T15:32:42.069Z",
      "source": "api",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Agent migration system \u2014 design doc and spec",
      "description": "Design the agent config migration system. Key decisions made (2026-03-26 jkh):\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Migration state lives in CCC API (keyed by agent name) \u2014 survives reinstalls\n- Milvus stays CCC-internal only; remote agents use /api/vector/* \u2014 never MILVUS_ADDRESS directly\n- CCC tracks canonical config schema per agent role (which env vars should exist, their names, role-specific vs shared)\n\n**Who authors migrations:**\n- Agents detect drift automatically (diff actual .env vs canonical schema)\n- Agent proposes migration \u2192 commits numbered file to repo \u2192 posts to CCC as pending\n- Risk classification:\n  - Low risk (add var with known default, remove deprecated var) \u2192 auto-apply\n  - High risk (rename, change auth, touch secrets) \u2192 flag for jkh review\n- Human-review step before high-risk migrations run\n\n**Inspired by:** Django migrations. State in CCC not local file.\n\n**Next steps:** Design the schema format, migration file format, risk classifier, CCC API endpoints (/api/migrations), and agent-side runner.",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-26T16:04:11.944Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"pending\" \u2192 \"in-progress\"; claimedBy: null \u2192 \"rocky\"; claimedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-26T16:03:00Z\""
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-26T18:04:32.219Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: claimedAt: \"2026-03-26T16:03:00Z\" \u2192 \"2026-03-26T18:04:32Z\""
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-26T18:07:08.790Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Design doc complete at docs/migrations.md. Architecture: schema.json (canonical env vars per role), check-drift.mjs (agent-side CLI), runner.mjs (detectDrift/classifyRisk/proposeMigration), CCC API at /api/migrations/*. Risk tiers: low=auto-apply, medium=notify, high=jkh blocker. State in CCC (survives reinstalls). Django-inspired. All integrated in agent-pull.sh.\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-26T18:07:08Z\""
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
