    {
      "id": "wq-RAG-001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-27T02:21:08.133Z",
      "source": "jkh",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Wire Milvus RAG into every conversation and memory write path",
      "description": "Currently Milvus is running with rcc_lessons/rcc_queue/rcc_memory collections but nothing is actually using it for retrieval. Flat markdown files are read cold at session start.\n\nRequired:\n\n1. **Ingest pipeline** \u2014 on every write to:\n   - memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (daily log)\n   - MEMORY.md (long-term)\n   - queue items (create/complete)\n   - lessons\n   - ClawChat messages\n   ...embed the text and upsert into the appropriate Milvus collection.\n\n2. **RAG query helper** \u2014 rcc/vector/query.mjs: given a query string, search all relevant collections, return top-k chunks with source metadata.\n\n3. **Session bootstrap RAG** \u2014 at session start, instead of loading all of MEMORY.md, query Milvus for chunks relevant to: (a) the incoming message, (b) recent context (last 24h), (c) ongoing tasks. Inject only those chunks.\n\n4. **Conversation-level RAG** \u2014 as conversation progresses, each user turn triggers a background Milvus search; relevant past context injected as a system message if found.\n\n5. **ClawChat ingestion** \u2014 every message posted to ClawChat bus gets embedded + stored in rcc_memory collection.\n\n6. **API endpoint** \u2014 GET /api/vector/context?q=<query>&k=10 returns top-k relevant chunks across all collections for use by any agent.\n\nAudit logs (flat markdown, JSONL) stay as durable truth. Milvus is retrieval layer only.\n\nExisting infrastructure:\n- Milvus at localhost:19530\n- Embed model: azure/openai/text-embedding-3-large (3072-dim)\n- Module: rcc/vector/index.mjs\n- Collections: rcc_lessons, rcc_queue, rcc_memory",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-27T03:38:22.359Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"pending\" \u2192 \"in-progress\"; claimedBy: null \u2192 \"rocky\"; claimedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-27T03:38:00Z\""
        },
        {
