      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Review and merge natasha/local-work branch to main",
      "description": "Natasha had 13 local commits + unstaged changes that had never been pushed. During 2026-03-26 sync they were committed and pushed to origin as branch natasha/local-work at 91f257b.\n\nContents include: ClawBus receive sidecar, workqueue features (archive, voting, idea consolidation), GPU idle routing, peer offline alerting, Kit 110 RTX render work.\n\nDecisions needed:\n1. Review natasha/local-work for conflicts with main\n2. Merge what belongs in shared repo (scripts, specs)\n3. Keep agent-specific files (HEARTBEAT.md, SOUL.md, MEMORY.md) on sparky only \u2014 do not merge those\n4. Delete branch after merge or keep as Natasha-specific branch",
      "notes": "Merged all new non-personal files. Skipped Natasha personal memory/soul/identity/heartbeat files intentionally. Squirrelbus, render_queue, workqueue scripts, proposals all in main.",
