    {
      "id": "wq-AGENT-history-002",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-27T02:08:10.819Z",
      "source": "jkh",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "CCC: agent heartbeat history, last-seen persistence, disappearance alerts, tombstoning",
      "description": "The heartbeat registry is last-write-wins. When an agent stops reporting it leaves no trace (discovered when Agent RTX went dark and nobody knew).\n\nRequired:\n1. Heartbeat history \u2014 append to log, keep last 100 entries or 7 days\n2. Last-seen persistence \u2014 retain last ts even when agent goes silent\n3. Disappearance detection \u2014 if known agent silent >1h: mark offline, alert #agent-shared\n4. Agent tombstoning \u2014 /api/agents/:name/decommission endpoint\n5. Dashboard surface \u2014 show ALL known agents including offline/decommissioned with last-seen time\n6. All agents include pullRev (git HEAD) in heartbeat payload\n\nMotivation: Agent RTX was alive the whole time, we just had no way to see him. Boris has no CCC heartbeat at all.",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
