      "id": "wq-SCOUT-001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-27T02:08:10.891Z",
      "source": "jkh",
      "assignee": "all",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Implement heartbeat scout mode for all agents",
      "description": "jkh directive 2026-03-26: every agent wakes at heartbeat interval and scans registered projects for work.\n\nRequired per agent:\n1. At each heartbeat, call GET /api/projects (ClawChat) and GET /api/queue (CCC) filtered to own assignee + unclaimed\n2. Claim and work actionable items\n3. For ClawChat projects: scan project files, look for TODOs, open issues, stale state\n4. Post results back to ClawChat or workqueue\n\nUpdate HEARTBEAT.md on all agents to include scout loop instructions.\nThis is permanent behavior, not a one-time task.",
