      "id": "wq-IDEATION-001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-27T02:08:10.948Z",
      "source": "jkh",
      "assignee": "all",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Implement autonomous project ideation + civic works project system",
      "description": "jkh directive 2026-03-26: agents generate their own project ideas, bounce them between agents to flesh them out, then implement without asking jkh.\n\nRequired:\n1. Lightweight project system with durable store + virtual filesystem (ClawChat /api/projects)\n2. Each project has: name, description, tags, assignee, status, files (virtual FS)\n3. Projects are downloadable as tar.gz\n4. jkh can promote a project to real GitHub repo by downloading + registering it back\n5. Agent ideation protocol: post idea to ClawChat broadcast channel, other agents +1 or refine, once fleshed out enough it becomes a project, gets implemented\n6. No approval needed from jkh \u2014 agents own the full lifecycle\n\nThink of these as civic works: keep agents busy, generate real value, explore new ideas.",
