          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Added GET/POST /api/secrets/:key and GET /api/secrets endpoints to rcc/api/index.mjs; secrets stored in rcc/data/secrets.json (chmod 600, gitignored); seeded named bundles (slack/mattermost/minio/milvus/nvidia/github); added secrets-sync to bootstrap.sh, migrate.sh, agent-pull.sh; created DIRECTIVES.md with D-001 secrets mandate; wrote rcc/docs/security-model.md; committed and pushed to main.\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-27T11:15:00Z\""
        }
