          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: \"Claimed by Natasha \u2014 spawning coding agent to build test suite\" \u2192 \"Test suite written and pushed to natasha/merge-sparky-2026-03-27 (commit 39770a3). 5 files: api.test.mjs (36 tests, 36/36 pass), integration.test.mjs (live server bootstrap flow), ui.test.mjs (dashboard smoke tests), run-tests.sh (CI runner), BUGS.md (9 bugs documented). Key findings: GET /api/bootstrap regression NOT fully fixed despite commit 2302f1c \u2014 still returns 401 without auth header. Missing /api/secrets endpoint. ideation module missing entirely. vector/index.mjs export name mismatch. setInterval prevents clean process exit after tests. Full bug list in rcc/tests/BUGS.md.\""
