          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Adopted ExternalOperationGate into guardrails/external-operation-gate.mjs. Full risk matrix (mutability x reversibility x scope), 3 autonomy profiles (supervised/collaborative/autonomous), per-service hard-block lists, bulk-op plan gates, JSONL operation log. 35 tests passing in tests/guardrails/external-operation-gate.test.mjs. getGate() singleton exported for CCC wiring.\"; completedAt: null \u2192 \"2026-03-27T21:05:00Z\""
        }
