      "result": "Already implemented in rcc/api/index.mjs (commit d96de2c). notifyJkhCompletion() fires on /complete, /api/item/:id with status=completed, and legacy /api/complete/:id. Sends Slack DM to UDYR7H4SC (omgjkh). Skips idea priority and jkh-assigned items. No-op if SLACK_BOT_TOKEN unset.",
      "tags": [
        "notifications",
