    {
      "id": "wq-API-1774666191679",
      "itemVersion": 5,
      "created": "2026-03-28T02:49:51.679Z",
      "source": "api",
      "assignee": "rocky",
      "priority": "medium",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Dashboard v2: CRUD \u2014 projects, tasks, conversations, users, agent history",
      "description": "The v2 dashboard needs full CRUD for all core entities. This is the data layer that backs the Kanban, Projects, Calendar, and Overview pages.\n\nEntities required:\n\n1. PROJECTS \u2014 Create/read/update/delete. Fields: id, name, description, repoUrl, slackChannels[], tags[], status (active/archived), createdAt, updatedAt. Already partially exists in repos.json/projects.json \u2014 formalize and expose via API.\n\n2. TASKS (queue items) \u2014 Already exists. Add: type (bug/idea/feature/proposal/task), blockedBy[], blocks[], needsHuman, needsHumanReason. Expose full CRUD via API (POST/GET/PATCH/DELETE /api/item/:id).\n\n3. CONVERSATIONS \u2014 Log of cross-agent and human-agent conversations. Fields: id, participants[], channel (slack/mattermost/telegram/clawbus), projectId (optional), messages[{ts, author, text}], summary (LLM-generated), tags[]. API: GET /api/conversations?project=X&agent=Y, POST /api/conversations, GET /api/conversations/:id.\n\n4. USERS (humans) \u2014 Registry of human participants. Fields: id, name, handle, channels{slack, telegram, mattermost}, role (owner/collaborator/observer), lastSeen, notes. API: GET /api/users, POST /api/users, PATCH /api/users/:id. jkh is always present (seeded from OPERATOR_HANDLE).\n\n5. AGENT HISTORY \u2014 Per-agent audit trail beyond heartbeats. Fields: agentName, event (heartbeat/claim/complete/fail/crash/restart/deploy), ts, detail, pullRev. API: GET /api/agents/:name/history (already exists as heartbeat-only \u2014 extend to full event log). Write path: agents POST to /api/agents/:name/events.\n\nAPI surface:\n- POST/GET /api/projects\n- PATCH/DELETE /api/projects/:id\n- GET /api/conversations (filter: project, agent, channel, since)\n- POST /api/conversations\n- GET /api/conversations/:id\n- POST /api/users, GET /api/users, PATCH /api/users/:id\n- POST /api/agents/:name/events\n- GET /api/agents/:name/history (extended)\n\nStorage: JSON files in rcc/api/data/ (same pattern as existing queue/agents). Migrate to SQLite if/when file I/O becomes a bottleneck (not now).\n\nAll endpoints auth-gated except GET /api/users (public read).",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
