      "title": "Publish GPU benchmark baseline to MinIO (agents/natasha/gpu-baseline.json)",
      "description": "wq-API-1774562930134 was marked completed but the gpu-baseline.json was never published to MinIO. Sparky has NVIDIA GB10 Blackwell with 128GB unified memory and CUDA available (confirmed 2026-03-28). Run: matrix multiply throughput (FP16/BF16), TensorRT inference latency (test with onnxruntime or torch), memory bandwidth (pytorch or cuBLAS), and ollama nomic-embed-text throughput. Publish result to MinIO at agents/natasha/gpu-baseline.json. CCC routing can then prefer natasha for heavy GPU inference vs Boris for multi-GPU vLLM serving.",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "gpu",
      "journal": [
