          "author": "natasha",
          "type": "claim",
          "text": "Claimed"
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-28T15:20:34.521Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Done. Rust 1.94.1 + trunk 0.21.14 + sccache 0.14.0 installed on sparky aarch64. sccache wired via ~/.cargo/config.toml. Build times: cold ~26s, post-clean with warm cache ~9s, incremental <1s. ~50% cache hit on first post-clean rebuild, near 100% on subsequent. BUILD.md added. Committed a8ea0d4.\""
        }
      ],
