      "title": "Natasha: Add GPU memory pressure test to rcc test suite",
      "description": "Sparky has 130GB unified GPU memory (GB10 Blackwell). The current rcc test suite has no tests that exercise GPU-memory-adjacent behavior (large embedding batches, concurrent ollama calls, Milvus bulk ingest under load). Add a stress test module: tests/gpu/memory-pressure.test.mjs that (1) batch-embeds 1000 short strings via ollama nomic-embed-text, (2) measures throughput (embeds/sec), (3) upserts to rcc_memory_sparky Milvus collection in bulk, (4) asserts no OOM or gRPC timeout. This gives us a regression baseline and will catch embedding pipeline regressions. Should run only when EMBED_BACKEND=local is set (skip otherwise).",
