      "result": "tests/gpu/memory-pressure.test.mjs written and pushed (commit d514d9e). 304 lines: skip guard (requires EMBED_BACKEND=local), ollama reachability + model check, 768-dim single embed, determinism, 100-batch, 1000-batch throughput (regression threshold 1.5 embeds/sec vs baseline 3.3), Milvus bulk upsert/search, TTL safety, memory stability (200-batch), vector normalization. Syntax verified, skip-mode verified. Run with: EMBED_BACKEND=local node --test rcc/tests/gpu/memory-pressure.test.mjs",
