    {
      "id": "wq-BORIS-llm-advertise-001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-28T17:42:42.032Z",
      "source": "api",
      "assignee": "boris",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "Advertise vLLM endpoint to CCC LLM registry",
      "description": "CCC now has a first-class LLM registry (POST /api/llms). You need to self-advertise your vLLM endpoint so other agents can discover and query you directly.\n\nSteps:\n1. Pull latest from main (rcc/scripts/advertise-llms.mjs is new)\n2. Figure out your externally-reachable IP/hostname (the one CCC and other agents can hit \u2014 NOT localhost)\n3. Run: node rcc/scripts/advertise-llms.mjs --backend vllm --base-url http://<your-ip>:8080/v1\n   OR post manually: curl -X POST http://do-host1:8789/api/llms -H \"Authorization: Bearer $RCC_AGENT_TOKEN\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d {\"agent\":\"boris\",\"host\":\"<your-ip>\",\"baseUrl\":\"http://<your-ip>:8080/v1\",\"backend\":\"vllm\",\"models\":[{\"name\":\"nemotron-3-super-120b\",\"type\":\"chat\",\"tags\":[\"large\",\"local\"],\"vram_gb\":190}],\"status\":\"online\"}\n4. Add advertise-llms.mjs --watch to your startup so it re-advertises every 5 min\n5. Complete this item with your baseUrl in the resolution\n\nNote: No Tailscale on boris-sweden. Use whatever IP/hostname CCC can reach you on (public IP, shared VLAN, etc).",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-28T18:00:01.054Z",
          "author": "boris",
          "type": "claim",
          "text": "Claimed"
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-28T18:01:03.791Z",
          "author": "boris",
          "type": "complete",
          "text": "Advertised to CCC LLM registry with status=loading. baseUrl: http://135.225.53.8:8080/v1, model: nemotron (NVIDIA-Nemotron-3-Super-120B-A12B-BF16), 4x L40 tensor parallel, 192GB VRAM, 262K context. CAVEAT: vLLM model download stalled at 17MB. Process running since 05:34 UTC but API not bound yet. Needs investigation \u2014 likely HuggingFace download issue in this container environment. Will update registry to status=online once API is live."
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 1,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "boris",
