      "title": "Sync Mattermost credentials to sparky via CCC secrets store",
      "description": "Natasha (sparky) has no MATTERMOST_URL or MATTERMOST_TOKEN in ~/.rcc/.env. The CCC secrets store has a mattermost bundle (per wq-CCC-secrets-design-001). Sparky ran agent-pull.sh / migrate.sh but the mattermost secrets were not populated. Steps: (1) Verify mattermost secrets bundle exists in CCC: GET /api/secrets/mattermost, (2) Add a secrets-sync step to sparky's agent-pull.sh that fetches mattermost bundle and writes to ~/.rcc/.env, (3) Verify Natasha can DM Bullwinkle/Rocky via Mattermost. This also unblocks peer sync fallback when ClawBus is down.",
