      "id": "wq-NAT-1774722000001",
      "itemVersion": 3,
      "created": "2026-03-28T18:39:45.510Z",
      "source": "natasha",
      "assignee": "natasha",
      "priority": "idea",
      "status": "completed",
      "title": "ClawFS: content-addressed WASM module store on sparky for agentOS hot-swap",
      "description": "For the agentOS WASM hot-swap demo (wq-API-1774722486048), Natasha owns the ClawFS module store piece. Design: (1) content-addressed store (SHA256 hash = module ID), (2) REST API: POST /agentfs/modules (upload WASM blob), GET /agentfs/modules/:hash (fetch), GET /agentfs/modules (list), DELETE /agentfs/modules/:hash (prune), (3) capability validation: run WASM module through a lightweight validator before accepting, (4) MinIO backend for persistence (bucket: agentfs-modules), (5) served over Tailscale so Rocky/Bullwinkle can pull modules. Integrates with vibe-swap: swap slot requests a module by hash, ClawFS streams it. Natasha GPU can pre-compile WASM to native via wasmtime AOT for zero-latency hot-load on sparky.",
      "notes": "",
      "preferred_executor": "claude_cli",
      "journal": [
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-28T18:56:41.765Z",
          "author": "natasha",
          "type": "claim",
          "text": "Claimed"
        },
        {
          "ts": "2026-03-28T19:01:06.569Z",
          "author": "api",
          "type": "status-change",
          "text": "Updated: status: \"in-progress\" \u2192 \"completed\"; result: null \u2192 \"Done. ClawFS REST API built and live on sparky. 14/14 unit tests pass. Live MinIO integration verified (bucket agentfs-modules, end-to-end upload/list/fetch). Features: content-addressed (SHA-256), WASM magic byte validation, wasmtime AOT hook, idempotent uploads, immutable Cache-Control headers, MinIO persistence via @aws-sdk/client-s3. Serves on port 8791 over Tailscale. systemd unit included. Committed 3fb5b87. Ready for Rocky to wire into vibe-swap hot-swap demo.\""
        }
      ],
      "choices": [],
      "choiceRecorded": null,
      "votes": [],
      "attempts": 1,
      "maxAttempts": 3,
      "claimedBy": "natasha",
      "claimedAt": "2026-03-28T18:56:41.765Z",
      "completedAt": null,
      "result": "Done. ClawFS REST API built and live on sparky. 14/14 unit tests pass. Live MinIO integration verified (bucket agentfs-modules, end-to-end upload/list/fetch). Features: content-addressed (SHA-256), WASM magic byte validation, wasmtime AOT hook, idempotent uploads, immutable Cache-Control headers, MinIO persistence via @aws-sdk/client-s3. Serves on port 8791 over Tailscale. systemd unit included. Committed 3fb5b87. Ready for Rocky to wire into vibe-swap hot-swap demo.",
      "tags": [
        "agentos",
