      "title": "ClawFS: health endpoint + startup smoke test in systemd ExecStartPost",
      "description": "ClawFS (sparky:8791) has a /health endpoint but the systemd unit does not verify it on startup. Add ExecStartPost: curl -fs http://localhost:8791/health || exit 1 to the unit file so systemd marks the service as failed if the WASM store is unreachable. Also add a one-shot pre-start check that verifies MinIO bucket agentfs-modules is reachable before accepting traffic. This catches configuration regressions (wrong MINIO_ENDPOINT, missing credentials) before the service is marked active.",
