      "title": "WASM UI: Axum server \u2014 proxy clawchat + add auth layer",
      "description": "Extend ~/.openclaw/workspace/rcc/dashboard/dashboard-server/src/main.rs:\n1. Add /sc/* proxy route that forwards to clawchat backend (localhost:8790 or configurable via SC_URL env var). Mirror the existing /api/* and /bus/* proxy patterns.\n2. Add a lightweight bearer token auth layer: read RCC_AGENT_TOKEN from env, require it on mutating endpoints (/sc/api/messages POST, /api/* POST/PATCH/DELETE). GET endpoints remain open (or optionally gated by a separate READ_TOKEN).\n3. Serve everything on 0.0.0.0:8791 (current port) \u2014 the canonical single entry point.\n4. Add health endpoint at /health that returns server uptime, WASM build hash (from dist/index.html), and CCC connectivity status.\n5. Update Trunk.toml proxy config to match.",
